<!doctype html><html><head><meta charset='utf-8'><meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width,initial-scale=1'><title>UNBOUND Movement Library v1 Review</title><style>:root{color-scheme:dark;--bg:#070a0e;--panel:#101821;--panel2:#0c1219;--ink:#effaff;--muted:#93a9b3;--line:#22313c;--cyan:#39d7e8}body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif}main{max-width:1260px;margin:0 auto;padding:34px 20px 70px}h1{font-size:42px;margin:0 0 8px}h2{margin:34px 0 12px;color:#d8f8ff}p{color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(190px,1fr));gap:12px;margin:20px 0}.card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;padding:14px}.num{font-size:30px;font-weight:850;color:var(--cyan)}.label,.small{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}.pill{display:inline-block;padding:3px 8px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;margin:2px;background:var(--panel2);font-size:12px}.good{color:#bff8ca}.warn{color:#ffe0a3}details{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;background:rgba(16,24,33,.6)}summary{cursor:pointer;padding:14px 16px;font-weight:800;color:var(--cyan)}details>div{padding:0 14px 14px}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12.5px}th,td{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:8px;text-align:left;vertical-align:top}th{position:sticky;top:0;background:#0b1118;color:#d8f8ff}</style></head><body><main><h1>UNBOUND Movement Library v1 Review</h1><p>Executable metadata for the canonical movement library: rank template, movement slot, targets, equipment, stat weights, substitutions, skill associations, and sensitivity flags.</p><div class='grid'><div class='card'><div class='num'>177</div><div class='label'>canonical exercises</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>5</div><div class='label'>rank templates</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>9</div><div class='label'>program slots</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>78</div><div class='label'>skill-associated</div></div></div><h2>Rank Template Coverage</h2><div class='grid'><div class='card'><div class='num'>63</div><div class='label'>Barbell Strength</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>44</div><div class='label'>Bodyweight Reps</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>5</div><div class='label'>Hold / Control</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>64</div><div class='label'>Machine / Cable Strength</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>1</div><div class='label'>Weighted Bodyweight</div></div></div><h2>Program Slot Coverage</h2><div class='grid'><div class='card'><div class='num'>23</div><div class='label'>Arms</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>6</div><div class='label'>Calves</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>19</div><div class='label'>Core</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>24</div><div class='label'>Hinge / Posterior</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>17</div><div class='label'>Horizontal Pull</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>23</div><div class='label'>Horizontal Push</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>25</div><div class='label'>Squat / Quad</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>21</div><div class='label'>Vertical Pull</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>19</div><div class='label'>Vertical Push</div></div></div><h2>Equipment Coverage</h2><div class='grid'><div class='card'><div class='num'>2</div><div class='label'>Band</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>20</div><div class='label'>Barbell</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>15</div><div class='label'>Bench</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>84</div><div class='label'>Bodyweight</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>2</div><div class='label'>Box</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>28</div><div class='label'>Cable</div></div><div class='card'><div class='num'>4</div><d